oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Headquarters building, Camp Forrest, Tullahoma, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the exterior of the headquarters building at Camp Forrest in Tullahoma, Tennessee. A large American flag flies out front by the walkway. A sign that reads "Headquarters / Camp Forrest" is visible on left. Features a divided back for correspondence on reverse.
